query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 10 AND q.view_count <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('boolean-logic',
'encode',
'flex4.5',
'graph-databases',
'jface',
'laravel-5.7',
'multi-tenant',
'odoo-9',
'repaint',
'semantic-ui',
'sidebar',
'swiftui',
'sybase',
'transformation',
'z-index');
